   <script language="javascript">
    function setLogo() {
 			setEvents();
 			
 			 //Footer position für ie<7 setzen
             if (navigator.appName == "Microsoft Internet Explorer" || navigator.appName == "Netscape") {
 					if (navigator.appVersion.indexOf("MSIE 7") == -1 && navigator.appVersion.indexOf("MSIE 8") == -1 && navigator.appVersion.indexOf("iPad") != -1 ) {
 						var st = (document.documentElement.scrollTop);
 						var he =(document.documentElement.clientHeight);
 						he = he + st - 26;
 						document.getElementById('address').style.position="absolute";
 						document.getElementById('address').style.top = he  + 'px';
 					}
 			}
 			
             if (!document.images.newsEndeSpacerImg) return false;
             var pt = 400;
             var avHei = 0;
             if (document.all) {
                 pt = (document.documentElement.clientHeight - document.images.newsEndeSpacerImg.offsetTop)-252;
                 avHei= document.documentElement.clientHeight;
             } else {
                 pt = (window.innerHeight- document.images.newsEndeSpacerImg.offsetTop)-65;
                 avHei = window.innerHeight;
             }   
                   
             if (pt < 0) {
 			    document.getElementById("logoKnill").style.bottom = pt - 68 + 'px';                
                         
             }
             
             
             //Prüfen ob nicht News + Events reinstehen
             if (!document.getElementById('newsliste489')) return;
             
             var hei = document.getElementById('newsliste489').offsetHeight + document.getElementById('newsliste674').offsetHeight + 278;
             if (avHei - hei < 100) {
 				document.getElementById("logoKnill").style.top = hei + 50 + 'px';                
 				document.getElementById("logoKnill").style.width="65px";
 				document.getElementById("logoKnill").style.height="28px";
 
             }
             
             
            
         }
         
         function setEvents() {
         	if (!document.getElementById('newsliste489')) return;
 			
 			var he = document.getElementById('newsliste489').offsetHeight;
 			document.getElementById('EventTitleImg').style.top = he + 228 + 'px';
 			document.getElementById('EventTitleImg').style.display='';
 			document.getElementById('newsliste674').style.top = he + 250 + 'px';
 			
         }
         
 			document.documentElement.onscroll=setLogo;
             window.onresize=setLogo;
             
             
             ol_width = 700;
   </script>
